Invocation Name: busy bites
des:
Busy Bites is your ultimate companion for quick, delicious, and healthy meal ideas tailored to fit into your busy lifestyle. Designed to provide you with easy-to-follow recipes, helpful cooking tips, and nutritional information, this skill ensures you never run out of inspiration for breakfast, lunch, or dinner.

Prerequisites:
Hardware Requirements: Busy Bites requires an Alexa-enabled device such as Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Echo Show, or any other compatible Alexa device.

Quick and Easy Recipes: Discover a variety of recipes that are both quick to prepare and delicious to eat.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
